data.description: Enjoy small-town living, close to all the conveniences of larger cities in this lovely 3 bed/ 2 1/2 bath home built in 2018. This home offers beautiful finishes, a relaxing sunroom, two-car garage with an extra door to the back yard. Guttering that fills water barrels/planters to water flowers. Home has extra insulation for energy efficiency and a heated/cooled attic with stairs that could be converted to extra living space. 6 miles to I-35, 10 miles to Norman, Ok.
